Background*
Mr. Hideaki Honma has been President and Representative Director at Escrow Agent Japan Inc. since April 2007. He serves as Consultant at Niigata Venture Capital Co., Ltd. Mr. Honma established Honma Hideaki Certified Real Estate Surveyor Office in February 1982. Mr. Honma served as the President of K.K. Chuo Chosa Sekkei since November 1985. He served as the Chairman and Representative Director at Chuo Group Holdings Co., Ltd. since May 2009. Mr. Honma served as a Director ... of K.K. IDU Sogo Jimusho (changed name to Mothers Escrow Co., Ltd. in January 2006) since July 2004.Read Full Background

