Escrow Services
















Our escrow specialists have the professional expertise and resources required to act as a neutral third-party agent in financial transactions. Many of the nation's leading law firms rely on our escrow specialists to provide timely, accurate and secure services. Our complete escrow services help your clients minimize risk in a complex environment.
Comprehensive Escrow Agent Services
In a market filled with uncertainties, escrow arrangements are an easily acceptable and versatile tool for assuring the safe, sound and efficient completion of a variety of transactions. An escrow agent will hold assets, invest funds, oversee distribution of funds and may handle tax reporting duties in order to fulfill the conditions of an underlying agreement.
Our full range of integrated escrow services includes document review, investment services, wire transfer and deposit services, payment and disbursement services, and detailed activity and asset reporting for all parties.
Experienced Escrow Specialists Support
Your dedicated escrow specialist within the Escrow Services group will have the experience combined with the responsiveness and efficiency required to manage your escrow transaction.
We specialize in the following types of escrows:

Indemnification 
Merger and acquisition 
Contractor retention and construction 
Private placements and subscription 
Class action, litigation and structured settlement 
Software licensing and source code 
Other business escrows 
Remediation and environmental protection 
Impoundment  
Real estate purchase and sale and 1031 exchanges 
Franchise

